planned features

for users:

    - view all public forums
        - create thread
        - view thread
            - reply to thread

    - view my forums / classes / workshops
        - create thread
        - view thread
            - reply to thread
        - sign up for class / workshop


for admins:

    - create public forum / class / workshop
    
    - view my classes
        - enrollment stats
        - add new event to calendar
            - attach files to event